1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All the sorrow between us.

2
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,039
Officers.

3
00:01:27,039 --> 00:01:28,640
What are you doing?

4
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:31,160
Arrest the suspect, Min Huishi.

5
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,580
Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

6
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:34,759
You...

7
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,479
Let go of me.

8
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:37,640
Let me go.

9
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:38,640
Stop.

10
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:41,960
Without any reason,

11
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:43,280
on what grounds are you arresting her?

12
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,720
Who are you?

13
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,780
Where is Lord Fang?

14
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:56,050
You're that girl from the Capital who caused trouble at the execution ground yesterday.

15
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,080
I am.

16
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,650
What do you want?

17
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:03,000
You're so arrogant for someone involved in a murder case.

18
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,720
We'll take you in as well.

19
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:05,690
Yes, sir.

20
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,720
You accuse people of being murderers on a whim.

21
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,120
Is this how you perform your duties?

22
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,840
You lowly woman.

23
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:25,040
How dare you obstruct official business!

24
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:25,800
Get them!

25
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,520
Seize them.

26
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,170
Let's see who dares.

27
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:33,000
[Hyah]

28
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,000
Greetings, Prefect.

29
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,000
Lord Jian.

30
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,520
You're here.

31
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,200
You didn't notify our Lord.

32
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,840
We have been remiss.

33
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,040
Good.

34
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:47,400
Very good.

35
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,000
If Lord Fang hadn't invited me,

36
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,400
I wouldn't have seen how imposing you look.

37
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,440
What happened?

38
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:02,760
Last night,

39
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:05,240
Cao Agou and Daxian's wife were murdered.

40
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:08,770
Min Huishi happened to argue with him during the day,

41
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:11,840
and someone saw her go out at night.

42
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:15,240
So, we misunderstood the situation.

43
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,320
Dead.

44
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,960
This wound...

45
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,600
looks like it was caused by a wild beast.

46
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,240
Lord Yingui.

47
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:53,700
Vice...

48
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,460
It must be Lord Yingui.

49
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,060
Yesterday,

50
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,760
I was temporarily assigned to the salt works yesterday.

51
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:02,040
I saw Cao Agou on duty.

52
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,240
He got a jar of good wine from somewhere,

53
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,240
and urged the brothers to drink.

54
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,120
Once we started drinking,

55
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,250
everyone got drunk.

56
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,640
When we woke up, it was already dawn.

57
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,880
Do you know roughly what time it was?

58
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,600
The Hour of the Ox.

59
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,920
The Hour of the Ox.

60
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:27,360
Entry to the depot requires registration

61
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,040
and surrendering the waist tag.

62
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,520
At the Hour of the Rat,

63
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:31,280
the depot is locked.

64
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,640
No one is allowed in or out.

65
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,280
There is a hole in the back fence of the salt works.

66
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,680
It hasn't been repaired.

67
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:43,040
It's for the brothers to visit the salt workers' homes at night

68
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,080
to find women to warm their beds.

69
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,440
This Cao Agou,

70
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,200
went often.

71
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,170
He was always going out to have fun.

72
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,400
A human life is at stake.

73
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:54,600
We will make a judgment after the autopsy results are out.

74
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:04,000
What brings Lord Xiong here?

75
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:08,600
The new Prefect, Lord Jian, is here for an inspection.

76
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:11,340
I didn't know. Please excuse my negligence.

77
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:15,160
My Lord, you have just taken office,

78
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,480
so you don't know the local customs.

79
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,000
In this area,

80
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,860
tigers and wolves run rampant in the mountains.

81
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:25,240
Wild beast attacks occur frequently.

82
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,450
These villagers are ignorant.

83
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:30,880
So they attribute it to ghosts and demons.

84
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,520
Hao Luo'er.

85
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,600
My Lord.

86
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:40,000
Didn't you see beast claw marks a few days ago?

87
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,320
Yes.

88
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:44,200
I did see beast claw marks.

89
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,000
Well...

90
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,280
The New Year is approaching.

91
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,520
Let's not cause panic among the people.

92
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,560
Just now,

93
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:54,880
the County Magistrate has already shared

94
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,810
Cao Agou's autopsy report with me.

95
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,659
I see that this woman's condition

96
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,120
is the same as his.

97
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,290
The location is not far off either.

98
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:07,240
They must have met for a tryst late last night

99
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,840
and encountered a wild beast.

100
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:12,640
Let's collect the body and bury it, so they may rest in peace.

101
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:13,640
Lord Xiong.

102
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,210
The Prefect hasn't spoken yet.

103
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,360
You are just a Salt Transport Official,

104
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:21,080
yet you are presiding over local administration.

105
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,040
The Governor General heard about this

106
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,570
and was extremely furious.

107
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,280
I am merely passing on a message.

108
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,680
Please do not blame me, Prefect.

109
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,240
Lord Xiong.

110
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:39,700
My Lord.

111
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,659
Lord Xiong.

112
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,200
Lord Xiong.

113
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,080
Are you all right?

114
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,159
I'm fine, I'm fine.

115
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,080
Good.

116
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,400
That is good.

117
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,400
What Lord Xiong said is quite right.

118
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:50,200
I, Jian, have just taken office.

119
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,800
I intended to

120
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,800
inspect the region,

121
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:59,409
but I didn't expect to encounter this.

122
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,840
Since the autopsy results are out,

123
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,200
then this case

124
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,040
is closed.

125
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:06,920
Good.

126
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:12,800
Since Lord Jian intends to inspect the region,

127
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,960
naturally, we cannot be negligent.

128
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,920
There is a courier station here.

129
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:19,800
Please proceed to the station to rest.

130
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:23,560
Thank you for your trouble, Lord Xiong.

131
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,820
Take the body away.

132
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,360
Move it.

133
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,200
Take care, Lord Xiong.

134
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,760
Corrupt officials!

135
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,040
First blaming tigers and wolves,

136
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,159
then blaming ghosts.

137
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,290
Taking us for fools.

138
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,159
Do not speak recklessly.

139
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,840
I haven't had a chance to introduce you.

140
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:53,960
This is my fellow disciple, Lord Jian Boning.

141
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,080
Lord Jian.

142
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:59,760
This is my student, Gu Lihan.

143
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:08,080
I anticipated the local officials wouldn't let it go,

144
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:10,160
so I invited Brother Jian to help.

145
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:15,690
Lord Fang, I have important matters to attend to.

146
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,080
I cannot stay.

147
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,800
When we meet in Jinzhou City again,

148
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,280
we shall drink and make merry,

149
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,680
and catch up on old times.

150
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,340
I won't see you off.

151
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,240
Take care.

152
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:32,280
Lord Jian, is this murder case closed just like that?

153
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,200
The case is closed.

154
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,260
You should go back.

155
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,679
Farewell.

156
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,640
Hyah!

157
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,640
Well done, Lord Fang.

158
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,420
Officials shielding each other.

159
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,690
You are all cut from the same cloth.

160
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:52,100
You call yourself an old hand.

161
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,700
Yet you can't see through this trick.

162
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,570
What do you mean?

163
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,840
Jian Boning just took office.

164
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,170
The local officials will be watching him.

165
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,800
So what can he find?

166
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,680
So you used a smokescreen.

167
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,240
You closed the case on the surface,

168
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,240
but investigated secretly.

169
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,440
You're smart.

170
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,680
You bet.

171
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:19,520
I just didn't expect the upright Master Fang

172
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,440
to use such tricks.

173
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,080
Did you kill Cao Agou?

174
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,240
Agou said yesterday

175
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,280
that you promised him

176
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:44,440
to service him in this shack.

177
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,320
Won't talk?

178
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:52,360
Talk, or I'll take you right in front of your man.

179
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,760
My body

180
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:18,080
has been ridden by Lord Ghost of Yama's Palace.

181
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:20,440
Aren't you afraid?

182
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,640
You must be thirsty after running around all day.

183
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,880
- Master Fang.
- Sister.

184
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:29,810
Have some water.

185
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,330
Where is Sister Hui?

186
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,300
In Jinzhou,

187
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:38,000
today is the day to invite the spirits home.

188
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
Sister Hui went to the graveyard

189
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,600
to burn paper money for her husband and sister.

190
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:46,780
They also scatter salt and burn incense at home to worship ancestors.

191
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:50,000
They say you can see footprints left by the ancestors the next day.

192
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,200
Strange, isn't it?

193
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:07,960
Coward, what a coward.

194
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:11,640
Greedy but gutless.

195
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:19,480
Lord Ghost said

196
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:25,720
everyone who bullied me

197
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:29,640
will be bitten to death alive.

198
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,640
What are you doing?

199
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,640
What are you doing?

200
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,440
But according to local custom,

201
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:49,040
visiting the grave must be done before noon.

202
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,760
Not at night.

203
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:51,840
Yes.

204
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:55,900
I did see many people going to the graveyard during the day.

205
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:58,160
But it's not safe at night.

206
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,800
Why did she go out alone?

207
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:01,880
How about this.

208
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,480
Yan'er, you watch the house.

209
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:04,880
It's late and the road is rough.

210
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:07,140
Master Fang and I will go meet Sister Hui.

211
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,290
Let's go.

212
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:25,600
Who is it?

213
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:40,960
That's not right.

214
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,640
I clearly saw a figure.

215
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,280
It can't just vanish.

216
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:08,840
What's wrong?

217
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,160
Are you okay?

218
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,720
I pricked my foot.

219
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:44,800
It was found on Daxian's wife.

220
00:13:58,440 --> 00:14:00,240
This is Golden Xiangfei Bamboo.

221
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,440
Not something ordinary families have.

222
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,520
Why is it here?

223
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,280
What are you doing?

224
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:17,880
It's dangerous here.

225
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,010
Let's go back first.

226
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,280
Little Marquis.

227
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:03,920
Hungry?

228
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:04,570
Here.

229
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:05,780
Eat something.

230
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,240
You eat.

231
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:24,720
A glance at misty rain, a dream.

232
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:31,600
Moonlight sings alone to the breeze.

233
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:35,520
Flowers bloom in the silent night, persisting.

234
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:39,240
The promise made by the youth yesterday.

235
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:41,120
Is for love,

236
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:44,960
writing a profound page.

237
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,520
A song of lute, a pot of wine.

238
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:52,000
A song of lute, a pot of wine.

239
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:58,960
Dancing alone in the clouds with rainbow sleeves.

240
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:02,720
Climbing high above the noisy world.

241
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:06,080
If you and I are together tomorrow,
